Purpose: Tell a user via email they've been invited to join an organization in Flareateam
Recipient: Invitee
Trigger: An existing user adds an unrecognized email address to an organization

Subject: You've been invited to join @organization in Flareteam

Body: Hi there,
@inviter_full_name has added you to the @organization organization in Flareteam. <Click here to log in> to get acquainted with Flareteam and help coordinate emergency responses.

See <this link for more information about flareteam>. 

Thanks,
The Flareteam Team

P.S. If this email doesn't make sense to you <Click Here to stop receiving emails from Flareteam>